text: Haya Maraachli () is a Syrian actress. She was born on 20 June 1997 in Damascus. In 2003, she made her first television appearance as a child in the series Abu El Mafhoumiyya. She became more famous after her participation in the series Women's Sessions. \- == References == == External links == * Category:Syrian television actresses Category:Syrian actresses Category:People from Damascus Category:Damascus University alumni Category:Living people Category:1997 births Category:Higher Institute for Dramatic Arts alumni Category:21st- century Syrian actresses Category:Syrian people of Lebanese descent Category:Syrian people of Turkish descent
